<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans von Wiesenthau zu Neuhaus an der Pegnitz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe der ohne Klage beschlagnahmten Habe des Armmanns zu Eichenstruth des Hans N., Vikar zu Heilig-Kreuz zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l29">Hanſen VVyſentawer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l30">cʒum Newenhauſe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l31"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans vns hat fürgelegt her Hans Vycarier cʒum heẏligen kreucʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l32">hıe beẏ vns / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Caplan / vvie Jr ~ <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu Aycheinſtrud </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l33">auf <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> gute doſelbſt / das ſein <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd hinvveg gefürt habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l34">vnd doch nẏe kein reht von Jm <expan>geuord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> habt / das vns von ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l35"><expan>vnfreuntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dunkt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>desſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Cl </del> Caplans </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l36"><expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> das ſein <expan>vvıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l37"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen Wysentawer czum Newenhause </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, uns hat fürgelegt her Hans, vycarier
                        czum heyligen kreucz hie bey uns, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> caplan, wie
                        ir <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Aycheinstrud auf
                            <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> gute doselbst das sein
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und hinweg gefürt habt und doch nye
                        kein reht von im <expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> habt, das uns von ew
                                <expan>unfreuntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dunkt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> caplans <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> das
                        sein <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
